attributes.title: STAR WARS in FALLOUT 4!! - Fallout 4 Mod Gameplay
attributes.description: A long time ago in a galaxy far, far away, Roach Queen discovered a relic of the Dark Side of the Force. She donned Darth Vader's helmet and, sensing its ultimate power, decided, "To heck with the rest of my clothes" and so she went nude through the Wasteland, chuckin' babies and beating up Macho Man Randy Savage. *Note: We implemented cheat codes to jump higher and run faster.

attributes.title: SUPERGIRL in Fallout 4! Mod Gameplay!
attributes.description: We really need some more mods to mod around with. Maybe a dinosaur mod where you can mod around on dinos? Or going with the Supergirl theme, a Calista Flockhart mod where you have to fight off 1000 skeleton lawyers? What about something where you shoot Preston Garveys? Our where your settlement is built out of a bleeding skullpile? I dunno, I'm not a modder

attributes.title: Let's Play - The Culling
attributes.description: Sexy teens, pitted against each other in a battle royale, sexy teen vs sexy teen. Things will really steam up, in a sexy sense, when these sexy teens start hunting each other down for sport, and for lust. We've pumped up the heat and humidity so these sexteens are all running around in shorts and sexy tank tops, sweating on each other, using bows and arrows and tongues to kill and love. A hot and slick morass of blood and twisted limbs and naked flesh, pressed against flesh. What better venue to fall in love than a Government Mandated Death Arena? SEXY TEENS

attributes.title: BLOOD AND GUTS - Killing Floor 2 Gameplay
attributes.description: A lot of you guys think that our gameplays are all improvised; that we make up what we say on the spot. That's not true. We put a lot of hard work into scripting out each moment of our videos. Here, for the first time, I'm going to share some of that old Funhaus Behind-the-Scenes magic with you. This is the first draft of our script for BLOOD AND GUTS - Killing Floor 2 Gameplay:  Elyse: Shit.  Bruce: Oh, shit!  Adam: What?  Elyse: SHIT!  Adam: Oh, no.   James: Look out.  Lawrence: I've got a gun.  Bruce: FUCK!  Adam: What this time?  (A beat)  Adam: Oh, Jesus.  Lawrence, James (Simultaneous): Shit  (Laughter)  Elyse: You guys are shitbuddies!  Adam: Huh?  Bruce: Fuckshit!  (Continues for 13 more minutes)

attributes.title: WE ALWAYS WIN - Overwatch Gameplay with Funhaus
attributes.description: Oh god, this is it. This is the last chance. If you don't watch this Overwatch video, I don't know if we can keep doing them. None - NONE - of our Overwatch vids have done well. I mean, we want our videos to get as many views as possible, but when this game isn't doing as many views as our crappy Shen Mue let's play, it may be time to rethink our strategy.  Which sucks! We love Overwatch! What's the problem? Do you not like watching it? Are you upset that you're not in the beta? Is it confusing? What is going on here? Someone tell me so I can fix it and we can make more Overwatch content! Please! PLEASE

attributes.title: Let's Play - Ultimate Chicken Horse with Funhaus!
attributes.description: Remember the show Lamb Chop's Play-Along? I bet you do. It was on in the early 90's (the best 90's) and hosted by Shari Lewis (R.I.P.). It had puppets, magic, lambs, an old woman, horses, coughing, jokes, let's plays, and a hand up someone's ass. This video has all those things too. Enjoy!

attributes.title: Let's Play - Party Saboteurs with Funhaus
attributes.description: Behold, a video in which we, Funhaus, play the hit new espionage couch multiplayer game "Party Saboteurs." James cheats. Bruce gets mad. Elyse thinks she's coy; isn't. Adam laughs. Joyous boy. Protect him. Internet fun. Friends and mischief. Not a haiku. Fin.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Gmod Murder with Funhaus
attributes.description: Sometimes you just need to stalk and pretend murder all of your coworkers.    Cause of Death: Hilarity!    Whatever, like you're so funny.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Lethal League with Funhaus
attributes.description: Chad introduces us to the hottest game of 2 years ago and releases all over everybody in the sickest way possible. Suuuuuurge!

attributes.title: Megaman 2 SPEED RUN RACE - Let's Play
attributes.description: The climax of our epic UnCivil War was unsurprisingly lacking in civility. Accusations were made. Insults traded. Chad even takes a few hits and he wasn't even there. Who will stand victorious? No one knows. Except us. And them. And everybody who watched the stream 2 weeks ago.

attributes.title: F*CKING LIAR - Gmod Murder with Funhaus
attributes.description: Oh my god, so much shrieking! Cr1tikal joins in on the killing spree this week but only seems to care about his damn cups.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Skyhook with Funhaus
attributes.description: It's the age old tale of Shark-Man vs Viking vs Cat-Boy vs Ninja, all playing basketball/quidditch while avoiding lava and with their grappling hooks.

attributes.title: BUSH HUNTER - Black Ops 3 Zombies Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Prepare for way more crotch shots and male scissoring than you would expect from a WW2-era zombie shooter.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Dead by Daylight Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Did you ever see "Jason X"? The one where the government freezes him then sends him into space for some reason. And then they thaw him out for some other reason. And then he gets blowed up and put in some sort of nano-healing chamber. And then he comes out but he's, like, bigger and half robot or something. And then they fight him in a holodeck reconstruction of Camp Crystal Lake. Someone gave them $11,000,000 to make that. Have fun at work, everybody.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Resident Evil 7 Biohazard Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Don't you dare deny it! You all peed your pants a little the first time you played the original. Yes you did. Really? Just me? Whatever. I hate you guys.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Depth Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: And the idea was, that Lawrence goes to Bruce and then he'd start poundin' and hollerin' and screamin' and sometimes the Lawrence would go away. Sometimes he wouldn't go away. Sometimes Lawrence, he looks right into you. Right into your eyes. You know the thing about Lawrence, he's got... lifeless eyes, black eyes, like a hentai pillow's eye. When Lawrence comes at ya, doesn't seem to be livin'. Until he bites ya and those black eyes roll over white.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Verdun Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Dearest Helen,  I hope this letter finds you well. The many nights since we parted have been long, and the days even longer. Despite the pains I am left with in your absence, I remain ever hopeful in our cause. I pray we may even defeat Jerry by Christmas if god-damn Elyse would stop getting her stupid Canadian foot caught in the barbed-wire like a dummy.  Yours eternally, Fredrick P. Estwith-Smythe

attributes.title: Let's Play - Dead by Daylight Starring Funhaus #2
attributes.description: Listen and understand. Peake is out there. He can't be bargained with. He can't be reasoned with. He doesn't feel pity, or remorse, or fear. And he absolutely will not stop, ever, until we are all dead.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Ragdoll Runners Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Continuing the proud, centuries old Olympic tradition of flailing around like your bones have dissolved and face-planting into a sand pit.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Push Me Pull You Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Just like Human Centipede but backwards and competitive and somehow more creepy.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Guts and Glory Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: That poor li'l toddler. No helmet. No belt. Getting stuck with arrows and chopped up by saw-blades. Someone might want to seriously consider calling Child Protective Services.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Party Hard Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: So much needless bloodshed. Sometimes people just want to make out on a toilet while sick beats play and a clown dances with a cowboy and chick dressed like Lady Gaga. Party-pooper.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Day of Infamy Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: The Funhaus gang finally gets to live out their dream of gunning down The Allies during World Wa- oh god I can't. I just can't do it anymore. Stay tuned to see The Greatest Generation blown to red mist, ya wierdos.

attributes.title: Let's Play - LASTFIGHT Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: France's most powerful fighters have all converged for battle. There's a deformed cyborg alligator-man, a topless plant-lady, a guy that shoots freeze-rays, a roided fish-ape, a bird-faced shaman, and... uh... a guy in OK shape named Richard.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Golf With Your Friends Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: I'd suggest that one of you fans out there make a swearing supercut of this video but it would probably only shave off about 40 seconds or so,

attributes.title: Let's Play - Attack on Titan Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: We need an idea for a new manga!Shoot. Uuuhhhh... of the top of my head, how about giant derpy grinning genocidal monsters eating medieval ninjas jumping around their town like a pack of god-damned spider monkeys?Here, take all of the money.

attributes.title: Let's Play What The Box? - Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Can you believe we made it through the entire gameplay without one ""box as vagina"" joke? You can? Congratulations! You're a big dumb idiot person.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Gmod Guess Who Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: "Outside the limit of our sight, feeding off us, perched on top of us, from birth to death, are our owners! Our owners! They have us. They control us! They are our masters! Wake up! They're all about you! All around you!"

attributes.title: Let's Play - Dungeon Punks Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Once more into battle, men! We must destroy the evil... Frog King? And the... those guys that are made out of sticks. And... wait...are those just hedgehogs. Do we really have to kill all those hedgehogs?

attributes.title: Let's Play - Can't Drive This Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Pop quiz, hotshot! There's three guys playing a game. Once they start playing, you all click and watch. If the video gets less than 300,000 views, I get fired. What do you do? What do you do?

attributes.title: Let's Play - Footbrawl Playground Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Next time you're out in the park enjoying a game of soccer with your buds, you must remain vigilant. The naked man prowls in the shadows, eager to pounce upon the unaware...

attributes.title: Let's Play - Gmod Extreme Football Throwdown Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: Just keep repeating: It's only a game... it's only a game... it's only a game.

attributes.title: Let's Play - Unloved Starring Funhaus
attributes.description: It's like GMOD and Doom made a hate baby in an abandoned orphanage while Dead by Daylight sipped champagne and watched from the corner.
